            "(56)^2 = (5/6)^2",
            "5^2 / 2 × 5 × 6 / 6^2",
            "= 25 / 60 / 36",
            "= 31 / 3 / 6",
            "= 3136",
            "Break the number into two parts (5 & 6) and apply the formula (a + b)^2 = a^2 + 2ab + b^2."
